From 35ff4ff5d8de94513cea70c1930e92579c4f7c99 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ganesh Kariganuru Mahabalesh <gkarigan@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 23 Jul 2025 10:22:09 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK:DP:wifi:ath12k: Export APIs required for
qca-wifi-nss-plugins

Introduce v2 versions of PPE DS WLAN operations that accept 
ds_node_id as input and export the corresponding symbols required 
by the qca-wifi-nss-plugins.

These additions retain the existing DS implementation. A follow-up 
cleanup patch will remove the intermediate v2 APIs once the 
NSS changes are fully merged.

Signed-off-by: Ganesh Kariganuru Mahabalesh <gkarigan@qti.qualcomm.com>
